<emphasis id="46DE290FFFEAFF8AEF884608FED2FA5B" box="[147,257,1391,1424]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">Habitat.</emphasis>
Rainforest.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="3CB0A696FFEAFF8AEF8846F9FBE4FA7C" box="[147,1079,1438,1463]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="7415F51DFFEAFF8AEF8846F9FBE4FA7C" blockId="8.[145,1348,1115,1935]" box="[147,1079,1438,1463]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis id="46DE290FFFEAFF8AEF8846F9FE4BFA7C" box="[147,408,1438,1463]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
Diet is said to include insects, birds, and plants.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="3CB0A696FFEAFF8AEF8A46A6FDB9FA15" box="[145,618,1473,1502]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" type="activity">
